Package: antisplit
Version: 1.2
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, apkeditor, apksigner, figlet, gum
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/termuxvoid/AntiSplit
Description: APK Split Package Combiner and Modifier
 AntiSplit is a tool designed to combine split APK packages
 into a single APK file and apply various modifications.
 Useful for repackaging and modifying Android applications.
